{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_53_02",
  "title": "鈴村優",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――二月二十七日　昼",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
          "delay": 532.8542233,
          "startTime": 1.3328542233
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1633.3333332999998,
          "startTime": 2.4333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "kanaさんkanaさん！　観ましたよドラマ～！\n『お嬢様、今日のコーデはいかほどに？』！",
      "startTime": 5.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "あ～『おじょコデ』ね……あざーす",
      "startTime": 9.0333335003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "もうほんっっっ……っまに最高でした！\nkanaさんの『ゴシップ大好きお喋りメイクさん』役",
      "startTime": 17.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "わずか一分ほどの出番、役名もないキャラながら\n傷跡を残さんと喋って喋って喋り倒すあの演技！",
      "startTime": 25.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "しかもぴゃーぴゃー喋ってても立てるべきセリフは\nきちんとキレーに聞こえるんですよね……！",
      "startTime": 32.5751003811,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱりkanaさん基礎がしっかりしてはるわ……！\nめちゃめちゃ勉強になりました！　あとそれから――",
      "startTime": 39.0348771844,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "待って待って待って、ダルいダルいダルい……\nあーもーなんでkanaの楽屋がこいつと一緒なんだよ",
      "startTime": 45.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "つーか嫌なこと思い出させてくれやがって……！\n散々だったんだからな、あのドラマの撮影！",
      "startTime": 53.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "「ここで面白いことを喋り続ける」だけ書かれてて……\nkanaのこと芸人だと思ってる訳！？　クソがっ！",
      "startTime": 61.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "つまりあれはほぼ全部アドリブ……！？\nていうか出演者の裏話、貴重過ぎる……！",
      "startTime": 67.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "はーい、この話終わりー、かいさーん\nお疲れっしたー",
      "startTime": 74.5195536415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "ええ～！　もっとお話聞きたいです～！\nあっ、うち今日誕生日なんです！　だからほら！　ね？",
      "startTime": 79.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "はー？　誕生日～？　そんなん知らんし……\n――いや、これは……使えるな……",
      "startTime": 91,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "分かった、それじゃあ裏話だけと言わず\nkanaがとっておきのプレゼントをあげようじゃん？",
      "startTime": 99.0333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4966.666666699993,
          "startTime": 104
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "こ、これは……！\nおじょコデ主人公、花子ちゃんのヘアスタイル……！",
      "startTime": 108.2666671753,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 10799.9994913,
          "startTime": 119.0666666666
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12533.332824699997,
          "startTime": 120.8
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "や～ん、お客様とってもお似合いですよ～\nこのまま記念にツーショいっちゃいましょ～ね～",
      "startTime": 116.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "はわわわわ……なんたるファンサ……！\nう、うちの！　うちのスマホでもお願いします！",
      "startTime": 125.9333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9033.328247000014,
          "startTime": 134.9666615803
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "いや後でデータ送るんでいいでしょ……\nんで、これをSNSに……ほい、投稿完了っと！",
      "startTime": 133.2666615803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "えーっと、「優ちゃん誕生日おめでと～！　kanaが\n出演したおじょコデ4話めっちゃ褒めてくれたの～！」",
      "startTime": 144.8666707357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "「誕プレ兼ねて花子ちゃん風ヘアアレンジ！\nシーズン2始まったら二人で一緒に鑑賞会しようね！」",
      "startTime": 152.9333496094,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "言うたからにはしてもらいますからね？\n鑑賞会、約束ですよ！　言質取りましたから！",
      "startTime": 162.2666615803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "はー？　やる訳ないでしょ。あ、でもさっきの投稿の\n反応良かったら考えてあげてもいいかも",
      "startTime": 171.9666615803,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8966.671752999986,
          "startTime": 180.9333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7533.33333339998,
          "startTime": 179.4999949137
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9633.325195299989,
          "startTime": 181.5999867756
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "うわ……しょーもないことしてたらもう時間じゃん……\nほら、スタジオ入るよ",
      "startTime": 179.3666615803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_02-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "かんしょ～かい！　かんしょ～か～い！",
      "startTime": 182.1333241779,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}